13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 1158, is
15 amended to read as follows:
16 Section 1158. A. On and after July 1, 2002, any person, before
17 engaging in the installation of individual sewage disposal systems,
18 shall first obtain certification from the Department of
19 Environmental Quality under such rules as may be promulgated by the
20 Environmental Quality Board. The provisions of this subsection
21 shall only apply to persons who install more than ten one individual
22 sewage disposal systems system per calendar year. As used in this
23 section, “individual sewage disposal systems system” means a sewage
